#      unified { code, claim, test } artifact noting agreements/
#      disagreements/unique-contributions per the v1x pattern
#
# This is the v1x knowledge-synthesis pattern adapted for code: every
# witness produces M18-shaped output by construction (mizaj 01 + atom
# 0007 baked into the prompt), the synthesizer enforces M18 coverage
# discipline at composition time. The downstream caller (opencode agent
# loop) gets code + claim + test as a structured artifact, not just code.
