# This is M3.32 (M18-disciplined fork-addition itself):
# - This SECTION FF is the burhan claim (Step 1 — claim first)
# - src/code-witness.test.ts will be Step 2 (test first)
# - src/code-witness.ts will be Step 3 (implement; tests must pass)
